{"type":null,"faqId":32887,"title":"怎样切换流光快门的四种模式","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body48096812\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750054__p23358283\">流光快门适用于拍摄动态图景和夜景，画面表现更好。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750054__p8897958\">在拍摄框下方有一个诸如<span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/ae25e_cknd8.png\" width=\"67.83\" height=\"21.945\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span>这样的按钮，点击该按钮可以选择流光溢彩的四种模式（车水马龙、光绘涂鸦、丝绢流水和绚丽星轨），选择完成后按钮中的文字就表示当前选中的模式。需要将手机放在支架上录制，根据效果自行确认录制时间。</p><p class=\"p2\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750054__p12972762\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/ae25f_niu3i.jpg\" width=\"252.3675\" height=\"409.9725\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span> <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/ae260_ehixv.jpg\" width=\"229.425\" height=\"410.5500016021728\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p class=\"p2\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750054__p49646001\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/ae261_24xbm.png\" width=\"253.365\" height=\"446.35787109375\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750054__p44160826\">* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</p></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0033750054","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748440000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10,PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-TL11H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":16,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"使用流光快门拍照,切换流光快门拍照的四种模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":n